description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 16, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 80, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [80 Votes, Common]
